    {"id": "c", "content": "<p><math><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mi>p</mi></mfrac></math></p>"},
    {"id": "d", "content": "<p><math><mfrac><mi>p</mi><mn>5</mn></mfrac></math></p>"}
  ],
  "keys": ["b"],
  "rationale": "<p>Choice B is correct. If each pound costs $5, then <math><mi>p</mi></math> pounds cost <math><mi>p</mi></math> times $5, or <math><mn>5</mn><mi>p</mi></math> dollars.</p><p>Choice A adds instead of multiplying. Choices C and D divide instead of multiplying.</p>",
